room_title: Escape room "Escape from Happy Acres" by Escape Room Adventures WNY in Buffalo
room_description: Welcome to Happy Acres! Dr. Ratched is confident that you, as the newest patients here, will enjoy our little institution very much. Our rules are simple: you can't leave. And don't even think about trying! You better get used to your new home. Oh, and by the way, your group is scheduled for your first round of shock therapy in one hour.
